 ture)
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20180522T200500Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20180522T202500Z
UID:21805@openstacksummitboston2017
DESCRIPTION:ECS Stack\, a product from EasyStack\, aims to provide simple 
 installation\, operation\, monitoring and maintenance for cloud users\, es
 pecially for user of Hyper Converged Infrastucture. ECS Stack includes ric
 h features\, like high availability for control plane\, upgrades online wi
 thout downtime\, perceptive visual orchestration\, application center\,etc
 . In the presentation we will explain how ECS Stack leverage the rich func
 tions from kubernetes and the de facto standard for privated cloud OpenSta
 ck\, and do an online demonstration.
LOCATION:
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:KEYNOTE: Containers Should Contain…Right?
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20180522T205000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20180522T211000Z
UID:21735@openstacksummitboston2017
DESCRIPTION:Containers are increasingly being used to deploy applications\
 , and with good reason - given their portability\, simple scalability and 
 lower management burden. But there’s one myth worth clearing up - contai
 ners do not provide an impermeable security boundary\, nor do they aim to.
 If you want to run untrusted code in containers\, how can you ensure it do
 esn’t affect other workloads? How should you set yourself up for multite
 nancy?In this talk\, you’ll learn about security boundaries\, the isolat
 ion currently provided at each construct in a containerized system\, and n
 ew projects that you can start using for stronger isolation requirements.
LOCATION:Vancouver Convention Centre West - Level One - Room 109-110
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Cloud Foundry and Kubernetes: Peaceful Coexistence
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20180522T211000Z
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20180522T212000Z
UID:21867@openstacksummitboston2017
DESCRIPTION:There has been some misconception that when choosing applicati
 on and services layers\, Cloud Foundry and Kubernetes is an “either/or
 ” choice. In reality they can work well together and complement each oth
 er. Come to this talk for a quick overview of this happy blend.
LOCATION:Vancouver Convention Centre West - Level One - Lightning Talk The
 ater
