 n-containerized. Many users/operators are keen to move their deployment to
  a containerized environment to various benefits of containers. But curren
 tly\, migration is a nightmare for operators.Kolla already provides produc
 tion ready containerized deployment for OpenStack services. It is the time
  to take steps towards solution which allow users and operators to contain
 erize their existing cloud without much hassle .In this presentation\, we 
 will discuss on the feasibility and challenges in migrating the cloud to c
 ontainerized deployment. We will also give a demonstration: **Partly conta
 inerized OpenStack cluster**.
