 penStack Helm + Prometheus + Grafana\nOS Layer – Global cpu usage\, Memo
 ry usage etc.\nKubernetes Layer – K8s Api health metrics\, ETCD performa
 nce metrics etc.\nOpenStack Layer – Resource utilization per project\, s
 ervice etc.\nLogging – OpenStack Helm + Fluentd + Elastic Search + Kiban
 a\nOS layer – syslog\, boot.log\, kern.log etc.\nKubernetes Layer – co
 ntainer Logs \nOpenStack Layer – OpenStack service Logs\n 
